This is a feature of the grid, as the last row has a single border and will be smaller. It's a styling issue, no business impact. It is possible to get around this by the application providing it's own style to the border as so:
.ag-row {
    border-top: none !important;
    border-bottom-width: 1px !important;
    border-bottom-style: solid !important;
}

